OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1776615077
OL,3,CSeven arrest over plot to target high-
OL,4,Cend retail sector
OL,6,FPolice have arrested seven people in
OL,7,Fwhat they say was 'a coordinated plan
OL,8,Fto target shops' across the country.
OL,10,FThe arrests were made over an alleged
OL,11,Fplot to disrupt high-end retailers and
OL,12,Fsupermarkets through organised
OL,13,Fshoplifting.
OL,15,FOfficers say the group had been
OL,16,Ftraining in Salford for non-violent
OL,17,Fdirect action, as part of plans to
OL,18,Fcarry out a nationwide campaign
OL,19,Finvolving theft from high-value stores
OL,20,Fand the redistribution of goods.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
