OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1776615077
OL,3,CSeven arrest over plot to target high-
OL,4,Cend retail sector
OL,6,FA man and six women were arrested in
OL,7,Fthe city on Sunday in a joint
OL,8,Foperation involving Greater Manchester
OL,9,FPolice and the Metropolitan Police.
OL,11,FAll seven remain in custody on
OL,12,Fsuspicion of conspiracy to steal.
OL,14,FAssistant Chief Constable Steph Parker
OL,15,Fsaid the arrests were part of efforts
OL,16,Fto tackle organised retail crime.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
