PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1776615077
OL,3,CSeven arrest over plot to target high-
OL,4,Cend retail sector
OL,6,F"This joint operation with the
OL,7,FMetropolitan Police has resulted in
OL,8,Fthe arrests of seven individuals who
OL,9,Fwe believe were planning to take part
OL,10,Fin coordinated national activity
OL,11,Ftargeting high-value retail stores,"
OL,12,Fshe said.
OL,14,F"We are taking robust action to
OL,15,Fdisrupt this type of organised
OL,16,Fcriminality, and it will not be
OL,17,Ftolerated in Greater Manchester.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@dO]vD@AOU
