OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1776615077
OL,3,CSeven arrest over plot to target high-
OL,4,Cend retail sector
OL,6,F"We take a strong stance against
OL,7,Ftargeted criminality such as this and
OL,8,FI would like to thank our Metropolitan
OL,9,FPolice colleagues for their
OL,10,Fassistance."
